	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In fact it does both.
<br />Normal audio is of course done by the NES, but the PowerPak emulatres FDS, VRC6, Sunsoft-5 audio for games (but it doesn't seem to support them on NSF mode yet). Also it doesn't seem to support MMC5 and VRC7, until I've missed some kind of update.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


